Key design decisions:
- **Separate classes per guest OS** to avoid the GRAVEYARD-documented class-scoped fixture collision issue
- **No parametrization for guest OS** - each OS in its own class for sequential VM teardown/creation
- **Tier 3** for extended-duration and multi-OS tests
- **Windows test omits arm64/s390x markers** (x86_64-only)
