## Repository Exploration Complete

### Documentation Findings
- Tests use `@pytest.mark.polarion("CNV-XXXXX")` for test case IDs
- Architecture markers: `arm64`, `s390x`, `x86_64`
- Tiering: `tier2`, `tier3` (tier1 not relevant, tier2 not needed per CLAUDE.md)
- Team markers: `virt`, `network`, `storage`, etc.
- Resource markers: `high_resource_vm` for Windows/heavy VMs
- All new tests MUST have markers; `@pytest.mark.usefixtures()` required when fixture return value unused

### Available Utilities (VNC/Screenshot-Relevant)

| Component | Import Path | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| `VNCConnection` | `utilities.vnc_utils` | Context manager for VNC proxy connection via pexpect |
| `collect_vnc_screenshot_for_vms()` | `utilities.data_collector` | Captures screenshot via `virtctl vnc screenshot` |
| `run_virtctl_command()` | `utilities.infra` | Runs arbitrary virtctl commands |
